Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.76,0:07:12.02,TV,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}[TV]只是我对你的感觉一直没变
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.03,0:07:15.16,TV,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}[TV]时针和人一样，都是不能回到起点重来的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.74,0:07:17.80,TV,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}[TV]我也一样已经不可能回到那个时候了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.05,0:07:19.80,TV,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}[TV]但是我还是喜欢你——
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.90,0:07:21.90,TV,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}[TV]我都说了我们是不可能的了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.28,0:07:25.28,TV,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}[TV]我为了忘记你足足用了3年的时间
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.29,0:07:27.50,TV,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}[TV]现在什么都不要说了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.62,0:06:58.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.04,0:07:00.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}欢迎回来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.56,0:07:03.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}还不去睡觉吗？明天你不是有约会吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.88,0:07:05.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}是啊，跟一个大帅哥
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.23,0:07:07.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}啊，对了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.98,0:07:09.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}那个借我，熏衣草香水
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.34,0:07:10.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}不行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.33,0:07:12.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}哼！小气
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.28,0:07:14.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}那不是小孩子擦的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.50,0:07:16.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}真嗣在房间里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.65,0:07:17.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}一直关在里面
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.32,0:07:19.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}看来他是不愿意去见他爸爸嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.35,0:07:22.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}不想见面的话，直说好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.14,0:07:23.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}日本人真是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.34,0:07:26.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}他也不是真的不愿意
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.08,0:07:28.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}这才是问题所在
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.43,0:07:34.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}滚回去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.76,0:07:41.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}你做得很好，真嗣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.29,0:07:47.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}真嗣君，我要开门罗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.58,0:07:55.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}害怕吗？怕跟你父亲单独见面
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.41,0:07:58.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}不可以老是逃避
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.31,0:08:00.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}自己不主动跨出第一步的话
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.15,0:08:02.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}什么也不会改变的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.96,0:08:04.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.38,0:08:06.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}从现在起就该好好想想
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.08,0:08:08.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}不只是最初的开始
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.04,0:08:11.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}之后的事情也很重要
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.36,0:08:15.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}总之，你明天去时要挺起胸膛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.60,0:08:16.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}因为你也要见你妈妈啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.85,0:08:18.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}那么，晚安了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.26,0:08:27.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}你买了明天穿的衣服对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.60,0:08:28.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}让我看看嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.30,0:08:30.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}你想看？很贵的喔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.54,0:08:32.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}品味比价格更重要
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.20,0:08:33.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}这你就不用担心了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.34,0:08:37.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}果然…是为了迎合加持先生的喜好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.77,0:08:38.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}哪有可能
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.84,0:08:39.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}早就没那事儿了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.51,0:08:41.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.02,0:08:42.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出发吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.57,0:08:43.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.82,0:08:51.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}将三个袋子置于内心…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.82,0:08:54.60,BGS,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}*人生中有三个重要的袋：胃(胃袋)、容忍(堪忍袋)、妈妈(お袋)
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.08,0:08:54.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}红色、蓝色、黄色的…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.28,0:08:57.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}啊，各位请自便
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.34,0:08:58.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,【加持良治先生】
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.08,0:09:01.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}小良没有来呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.63,0:09:05.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}那个笨蛋从来没有一次准时过的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.52,0:09:06.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}那是约会的时候吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.96,0:09:08.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}工作时可就不一样了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.74,0:09:09.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}哎呀，两位小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.20,0:09:11.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}今天比平常更加美丽耶
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.62,0:09:14.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}工作很忙，现在都还是分不开身啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.83,0:09:17.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}明明平常四处闲逛总是很闲的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.12,0:09:19.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}其它就算了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.09,0:09:20.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}但你那那脸胡渣不能想办法处理一下吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.32,0:09:22.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}{\a1}你看，领带都歪了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.13,0:09:23.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}{\a3}哦，果然
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.76,0:09:25.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}真是谢谢你了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.57,0:09:26.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}看起来很像夫妻哦，你们两个
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.86,0:09:29.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}你说得太对了，小律
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.63,0:09:30.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}谁会跟这种家伙像夫妇啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.92,0:09:47.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}相隔 3 年了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.06,0:09:48.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}离我们上次一起到这里来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.60,0:09:51.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}我那时候逃了出去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.95,0:09:54.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}之后就再没来过
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.98,0:09:56.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}当时我不能明白为何妈妈长眠于此
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.59,0:10:00.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}…现在却连面容也记不清了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.06,0:10:03.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}人类必须忘记回忆才能活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.15,0:10:06.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}但是有些事则是绝对不能忘的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.27,0:10:09.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}唯让我知道了那个无可取代的事物
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.67,0:10:13.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}我就是为了确认这件事而来到这里
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.85,0:10:17.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}没有照片之类的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.41,0:10:18.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}我没有留
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.86,0:10:20.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}这个墓地也只是装饰品而已
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.97,0:10:21.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}里面没有遗体
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.90,0:10:23.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}跟老师说的一样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.75,0:10:25.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}你把一切都舍弃了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.98,0:10:27.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}一切都存在于内心中
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.03,0:10:28.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}现在只要这样就够了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.47,0:10:34.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}时间到了，我先回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.17,0:10:42.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.96,0:10:45.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.21,0:10:47.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}我今天很高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.38,0:10:49.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}可以跟爸爸说话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.32,0:10:50.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.21,0:11:39.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}拉得不错嘛，你还有这手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.02,0:11:42.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}从 5 岁开始拉，到现在才有这种程度
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.46,0:11:44.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}也算不上有什么天赋
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.11,0:11:47.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}贵在坚持啊，我对你有点刮目相看了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.31,0:11:51.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}是老师叫我学的，其实放弃也无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.17,0:11:53.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}那你干吗还一直练到现在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.76,0:11:56.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}又没人叫我停呀
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.85,0:11:58.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}果然哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.01,0:11:59.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}这么早就回来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.75,0:12:02.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}还以为你要吃了晚饭再回来呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.71,0:12:04.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}是那男生太无聊了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.81,0:12:08.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}所以就趁等云霄飞车的时候溜回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.81,0:12:08.41,BGS,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}*云霄飞车（jet coaster）：一种飞行游戏
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.37,0:12:10.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}也不用这么绝吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.23,0:12:14.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}啊～　理想的男人只有加持一个呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.47,0:12:18.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}你这是说的什么话呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.95,0:12:20.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}我去一下洗手间
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.11,0:12:22.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}别找借口溜走哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.88,0:12:28.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}高跟鞋…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.89,0:12:32.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}好多年没有 3 个人在一起喝酒了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.07,0:12:35.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}美里会不会喝太多了？总觉得她今天话特别多
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.91,0:12:39.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}平时她会为了压抑自己浮动的心情而喝
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.87,0:12:41.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}而今天正好相反啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.75,0:12:46.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}不愧是曾经一起住过，说出来的话感受就是不同
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.85,0:12:51.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}虽说曾经一起住过，但那时葛城可不穿高跟鞋
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.57,0:12:54.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}在学生时代那可是不敢想象的东西啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.61,0:12:55.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}我也是个小鬼…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.50,0:12:59.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}与其说是同居，不如说只是单纯的住在一起吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.92,0:13:00.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}仅此而已
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.35,0:13:02.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}现实生活并没有那么单纯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.37,0:13:04.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}对了，这个给你，一点小意思
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.87,0:13:06.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}啊，谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.12,0:13:07.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}真有心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.20,0:13:10.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}只有对女性，工作就马马虎虎了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.80,0:13:13.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}真的吗？那对美里呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.95,0:13:17.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}已经败过一次了，我的原则是不打没胜算的仗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.76,0:13:19.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}我倒觉得你有胜算
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.57,0:13:20.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}那小律你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.82,0:13:22.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}我的原则是不谈自己的事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.22,0:13:24.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}因为无趣嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.50,0:13:26.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}葛城真慢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.15,0:13:28.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}该不会是去重新化妆了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.81,0:13:31.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}到京都干什么去了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.32,0:13:34.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}啊？这个土产是松代的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.73,0:13:35.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}少跟我装糊涂
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.11,0:13:37.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}好奇心太重当心引火烧身哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.90,0:13:40.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}这是作为朋友的忠告
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.47,0:13:42.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}我洗耳恭听
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.20,0:13:44.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}如果一定要烧身的话
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.56,0:13:45.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}{\pos(460,448)}我倒是想和你一起玩火
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.42,0:13:47.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}{\a1}那就去买好焰火再说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.78,0:13:48.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}你回来啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.66,0:13:50.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}你这种轻浮真是一点都没变啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.14,0:13:52.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}不，我变了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.72,0:13:54.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}活着就表示在变化呀
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.26,0:13:57.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}正如自我平衡与瞬态平衡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.26,0:13:57.27,BGS,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}*homeostasis(自我平衡)和transisstasis(瞬态平衡)
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.92,0:13:58.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.95,0:14:01.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}维持现状之力与改变现状之力
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.05,0:14:05.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}同时拥有这两种矛盾性质的东西才称为生物
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.33,0:14:07.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}是指男人和女人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.63,0:14:11.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}闲聊到此结束，我还有工作要做
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.61,0:14:12.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.43,0:14:12.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.87,0:14:13.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}真可惜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.10,0:14:14.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}再见
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.43,0:14:15.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.05,0:14:24.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}嗨，是小真吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.47,0:14:27.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}是我啦，现在在和加持君喝酒呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.35,0:14:29.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}对，今晚第 3 回了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.19,0:14:32.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}好的——好的，再见
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.32,0:14:33.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}是美里
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.33,0:14:36.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}嗯，她要晚点回来，叫我们先睡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.14,0:14:40.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}哎？这岂不是要到明天早上才回来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.40,0:14:42.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}怎么可能？加持先生跟她在一起啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.95,0:14:45.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}你是白痴吗？所以才会啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.28,0:14:53.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}年纪都不小了别像个小孩一样嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.50,0:14:56.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}真不好意思啊，都这个岁数了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.36,0:14:57.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}彼此彼此我也差不多
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.99,0:14:58.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.49,0:15:01.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}葛城你都穿上高跟鞋了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.41,0:15:03.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}时光的流逝真是好快啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.79,0:15:07.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}胡渣去刮掉嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.79,0:15:08.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}是、是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.75,0:15:11.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}让我下来走，谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.79,0:15:12.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.73,0:15:19.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}加持君，我变了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.81,0:15:21.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}…变漂亮了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.06,0:15:27.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}对不起，那时我单方面的要求分手
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.00,0:15:30.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}我还说喜欢上了别人…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.03,0:15:31.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}那是——骗你的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.44,0:15:32.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}你看穿了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.46,0:15:33.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}没有
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.11,0:15:38.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}我发觉了…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.33,0:15:41.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}加持君你很象我的父亲…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.09,0:15:49.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}我…想在其他男人的身上寻找父亲的影子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.31,0:15:53.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}当我发觉这点时…我好怕
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.87,0:15:55.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}害怕得不得了…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.57,0:15:58.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}和加持君在一起的事也是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.07,0:16:03.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}连我自己是个女人这点…都令我害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.32,0:16:09.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}憎恨父亲的我却喜欢上像父亲的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.42,0:16:12.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}后来想要斩断一切而选择了 NERV…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.96,0:16:16.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}但是，这也是父亲所参与过的组织
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.91,0:16:21.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}最后只能用向使徒复仇这样的借口来搪塞人们
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.87,0:16:30.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}这是葛城你自己的选择，不用向我道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.53,0:16:34.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}不是的！这不是我选择的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.30,0:16:36.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}这只是为了逃避
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.65,0:16:39.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}我只是想从“父亲”这个咒缚下逃避而已…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.44,0:16:41.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}和真嗣一样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.97,0:16:43.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}都是胆小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.61,0:16:45.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}真的很抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.00,0:16:48.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}现在才趁着酒势讲这些话
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.70,0:16:49.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}够了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.52,0:16:51.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}我真是个小孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.02,0:16:53.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}根本没资格说真嗣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.74,0:16:54.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}够了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.29,0:16:59.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}而且我还是个只会在需要时才想依靠男人的狡滑女人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.68,0:17:02.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}或许我那时候就是单纯地在利用加持君罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.01,0:17:03.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}真令人作呕
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.67,0:17:04.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}够了！不要再说了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.11,0:17:06.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}真是对自己感到绝望啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.45,0:17:31.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}…喂，真嗣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.66,0:17:32.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}来接吻吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.74,0:17:34.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}嗯，什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.60,0:17:35.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}接吻啦，接吻
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.15,0:17:37.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}你还没接过吻吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.08,0:17:38.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.23,0:17:39.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}那就来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.93,0:17:41.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.77,0:17:42.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}无聊嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.16,0:17:45.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}就因为无聊…哪有这样的…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.08,0:17:48.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}因为是母亲的忌日所以不想和女生接吻
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.49,0:17:51.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}担心她可能会在天上看到吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.20,0:17:52.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}不是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.74,0:17:53.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}还是因为你害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.10,0:17:56.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}我才不怕呢！不过是接个吻而已
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.46,0:17:58.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}牙齿刷过了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.95,0:17:59.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.58,0:18:00.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}那…开始喽
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.74,0:18:12.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}你鼻子呼气弄得我好痒，摒住
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.75,0:19:01.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}果然不该用这办法来打发时间
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.82,0:19:07.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}好了到了，坚持住
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.53,0:19:11.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}加持先生
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.47,0:19:14.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}哎——♡！加持先生
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.19,0:19:20.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}那么，我要回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.75,0:19:22.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}加持先生也在这里住一晚吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.68,0:19:24.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}这副样子我明天出去要被人笑死的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.15,0:19:27.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}哎——没关系嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.20,0:19:31.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}哎呀，加持先生你真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.21,0:19:31.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}…再见喽
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.49,0:19:38.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}薰衣草的香味…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.56,0:19:41.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}不好意思，葛城就拜托你们俩照顾了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.40,0:19:42.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}好的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.39,0:19:44.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}那么，晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.41,0:19:45.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.30,0:19:50.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}怎么了？垂头丧气的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.70,0:19:52.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}就因为跟你这种人接吻了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.10,0:19:57.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}那么接下来由女生回答
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.44,0:19:58.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}绫波
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.77,0:20:01.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}绫波今天又请假了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.05,0:20:03.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,【NERV 总部】
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.84,0:20:05.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,【深层地下设施 中央区域】
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.35,0:20:06.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,【中央教条区】
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.37,0:20:29.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,【同一时间 地下 2008 米】
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.49,0:20:31.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,【最终教条区】
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.09,0:20:45.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}呀…醉了两天现在感觉如何
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.56,0:20:46.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}托你的福总算醒过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.04,0:20:47.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}那真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.28,0:20:49.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}这就是你真正的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.47,0:20:51.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}还是说只是兼职而已
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.07,0:20:52.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}你指哪个
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.15,0:20:56.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}特务机关 NERV 特殊监查部所属的加持良治
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.95,0:21:01.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}同时又是日本政府内务省调查部所属的加持良治
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.92,0:21:02.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}暴露了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.05,0:21:04.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}不要小看 NERV
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.19,0:21:06.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}是碇司令的命令吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.01,0:21:07.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}是我自己的决定
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.49,0:21:11.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}再继续这份兼职的话，会死哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.57,0:21:13.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}原来碇司令一直在利用我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.71,0:21:14.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}死了也好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.26,0:21:17.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}但是对葛城你隐瞒了真相，真是对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.57,0:21:20.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}当昨天的谢礼算扯平了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.94,0:21:22.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}那真是谢谢了，只不过…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.58,0:21:25.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}司令和小律也对你隐瞒了一样东西
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.40,0:21:27.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}它就在这儿
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.14,0:21:35.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.32,0:21:39.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}EVA
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.37,0:21:42.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}不对！难道是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.91,0:21:46.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}没错，它就是第二次冲击之后所发生的一切的关键
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.17,0:21:48.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}也是一切的始因
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.56,0:21:50.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}亚当
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.68,0:21:53.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}亚当？第一使徒竟会在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.99,0:21:59.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}果然 NERV 远非我所想象的那么简单
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.71,0:23:10.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}傲慢的真嗣被吸进“狄拉克之海”
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.26,0:23:12.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}在所剩不多的时间里
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.90,0:23:14.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}他体会到了什么是绝望
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.98,0:23:17.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}下一回　致死之疾，然后…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.26,0:23:20.11,BGS,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}下集当然也有服务哦
